summary: This dumb ass video Jeffree posted literally proves my point.  They are all full of shit.  Ya’ll think he’s really just taking...
body:
This dumb ass video Jeffree posted literally proves my point. 

They are all full of shit.

Ya’ll think he’s really just taking the high road?? When has he ever? We’re not stupid Jeffree, sit the fuck down. The only reason he didn’t pull out the receipts is because he can’t win this game. If he comes for James, James is gonna come for him right back. He’s not used to that. Just like Tati, he never comes for anyone his size.
And another thing, all those people who constantly have to remind you how honest they are, are not honest. Those of us who are decent people, like not even good, just decent, we don’t need to reassure everyone all the time how truthful we are, it’s a given. So anytime I hear that bs, I know what’s about to happen. 
There’s no doubt in my mind he has proof of his claims, but he can’t show them. If this was to go on, it would turn into him and James exposing each other back and forth which would not end well for either of them. 
Anything Jeffree got on James, James got on Jeffree. They’re both ‘problematic’ they both pull the same shit, they got the same skeletons in their closet. There are no winners here. 
Jeffree chose to defuse this situation because that’s the only way to minimize the damage. All that bs about being ‘different’ now, bitch! things you said and did happened a few days ago, you’re not that different stfu. Not to mention you’ve been doing this same shit for the entirety of your career, you’re not fooling anyone. 
They are all full of shit, and I am so glad it’s out in the open. That entire ‘beauty community’ is everything but beautiful. I’m soo done. Bitches byeeee.
